name: Global X Artificial Intelligence & Technology Index ETF
longDescription: The ETF seeks to replicate, to the extent possible and net of expenses, the performance of an index that is designed to provide exposure to developed market, publicly listed companies that are positioned to benefit from the development and utilization of artificial intelligence (AI) in their products and services, as well as companies that produce hardware used in AI applied for the analysis of big data (currently, the Indxx Artificial Intelligence & Big Data Index).
